Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_mcr

The lower four bits of the modem-control register directly manipulate the outputs of the UART. The DTR, RTS, OUT1, and OUT2 bits are inverted and then drive the corresponding UART outputs: dtr_n, rts_n (UART0/1_RTS_L), out1_n, and out2_n.
